  "name": "Nagaraja COU1 — Total Knee Arthroplasty Tibial Insert Contact Stress Credibility Assessment (MRL 3)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for finite-element prediction of tibial insert contact stress in a total knee arthroplasty (TKA) implant system. COU1 evaluates whether the FE model can predict peak contact stress and contact area on the polyethylene tibial insert under physiological gait loading at Model Risk Level 3. All 13 credibility factors are assessed; achievedLevel meets or exceeds requiredLevel for every factor. Decision: Accepted.",
