    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Software quality assurance",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "rationale": "The FE solver (Abaqus 2022) is a commercially validated package with documented V&V procedures. An internal SQA checklist was executed confirming version control, regression test suite passage (>99.8% pass rate across 412 benchmark cases), and documented release notes. Input deck configuration management was maintained under Git with tagged releases. Achieved level 3 exceeds the MRL 3 requirement of level 2.",
