      "factorType": "Numerical code verification",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "rationale": "Patch test and single-element analytical benchmarks were executed for the C3D8I and C3D6 element types used in the tibial insert mesh. Results for linear elastic Hertzian contact between a sphere and flat plate reproduced analytical solution to within 1.2% for peak contact pressure. Benchmark cases archived in the project verification report.",
      "acceptanceCriteria": {
        "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/ac/tka-code-verif-ac-02",
        "type": "AcceptanceCriteria",
        "description": "Analytical benchmark (Hertzian contact) reproduced to within 5% for peak contact pressure using the element types and contact formulation deployed in the production model."
