      "factorType": "Output comparison",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "rationale": "Quantitative comparison between FE predictions and experimental measurements used mean absolute percentage error (MAPE) and coverage of experimental 95% confidence intervals. MAPE for peak contact stress: 8.3%; MAPE for contact area: 11.1%. All FE predictions fell within the experimental 95% CI for all 18 validation conditions. Comparison methodology documented per ASME V&V 40 Section 9.",
      "acceptanceCriteria": {
