      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "rationale": "Iterative convergence was confirmed for all load steps: force residual norm < 1×10⁻⁴ N and displacement residual norm < 1×10⁻⁵ mm for each increment. Contact penetration tolerance set to 1×10⁻³ mm. Automatic stabilisation energy ratio monitored and confirmed < 0.1% of total strain energy across all analyses, confirming negligible artificial damping contribution.",
      "acceptanceCriteria": {
        "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/ac/tka-solver-error-ac-08",
        "type": "AcceptanceCriteria",
        "description": "Force and displacement residual norms below solver convergence thresholds for all increments; artificial stabilisation energy < 1% of total strain energy; contact penetration < 0.01 mm."
      }
    },
    {
