      "factorType": "Use error",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "rationale": "Model setup was performed by two independent analysts following a documented modelling protocol (MP-TKA-FE-002 Rev B). An independent peer review of the input deck was completed by a senior analyst not involved in model construction, covering boundary condition application, material assignment, contact pair definition, and load step sequencing. All review findings were resolved prior to final analysis runs.",
      "acceptanceCriteria": {
